<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dance-n">dance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɑːns/    美 /dæns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 跳舞；舞蹈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a dance ﬂoor / class
舞池/舞蹈课</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What a pretty dance that is!
那是一种多么优美的舞蹈呀!</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-dance-party">2.★ <strong>[C] 舞会 (dance party)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>at a dance
在舞会上</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go to / hold a dance
参加/举办舞会</p></div>

<h4 id="3-u">3.★ <strong>[U] 舞蹈艺术：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an evening of music and dance
歌舞晚会</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>dancer /'dɑːnsə(r)/ n   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is a good / bad dancer.
他舞跳得好/不好。</p></div>

<p>dancing /'dɑːnsɪŋ/ n [U]   </p></div>